SELECT * FROM CalibrationData;

SELECT id, description FROM Project WHERE creation_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, nozzle_temp, bed_temp, print_speed FROM CalibrationSettings ORDER BY id ASC;

SELECT id, name, build_volume FROM Printer WHERE technology = 'FDM' ORDER BY build_volume DESC;

SELECT Project.name, Printer.name AS PrinterName, PrintQuality.quality_score FROM Project INNER JOIN PrintQuality ON Project.id = PrintQuality.project_id INNER JOIN Printer ON Printer.id = PrintQuality.printer_id WHERE Project.creation_date > '2022-01-01';

SELECT CalibrationData.calibration_date, CalibrationData.calibration_settings, Printer.name AS PrinterName FROM CalibrationData INNER JOIN Printer ON CalibrationData.printer_id = Printer.id WHERE CalibrationData.calibration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT Project.name AS ProjectName, COUNT(Printer.id) AS PrinterCount FROM Project LEFT JOIN Printer ON Printer.id = Project.id GROUP BY Project.name ORDER BY PrinterCount DESC, ProjectName ASC;
